front.title: Dantooine Operative
front.gametext: While at a Dantooine site: adds 1 to your Force drains there, is power +1 (or +2 if your thief is on Dantooine) and, once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one site to Dantooine from Reserve Deck- reshuffle.
front.lore: Corrupt Pacithhip businessmen. Report to the Empire on who makes contributions to the Alliance.
